OL,3,CTravellers to face disruption as
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel to shut
OL,6,FWhile GWR services will operate as
OL,7,Fusual between Pembroke Dock and
OL,8,FNewport, all services via the Severn
OL,9,FTunnel will be affected.
OL,11,FTrains from south Wales to London will
OL,12,Fbe rerouted via Gloucester, bypassing
OL,13,FBristol Parkway entirely.
OL,15,FThe disruption is scheduled from
OL,16,FWednesday, 3 July to Thursday, 18
OL,17,FJuly, and then again on the weekend of
OL,18,F27 and 28 July.
