OL,3,CTravellers to face disruption as
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel to shut
OL,6,FLimited replacement buses will be
OL,7,Favailable between Bristol Parkway and
OL,8,FNewport but only on Sundays.
OL,10,FTravellers needing to reach Bristol
OL,11,FParkway from south Wales will have to
OL,12,Fgo past Gloucester before heading back
OL,13,Fsouth and west towards Bristol.
OL,15,FDrivers are also warned the M4's
OL,16,FPrince of Wales Bridge will be shut
OL,17,Fwestbound overnight on Monday 8 July,
OL,18,FTuesday 9 July and Saturday 10 July.
