OL,3,CTravellers to face disruption as
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel to shut
OL,6,FThe M4 bridge will also close
OL,7,Feastbound on Wednesday and Thursday 10
OL,8,Fand 11 July 1 but the M48 Severn
OL,9,FBridge is due to remain open.
OL,11,FOn Monday and Tuesday 8 and 9 July,
OL,12,Fthe M4's westbound carriageway will be
OL,13,Fshut between 9pm and 5am on the bridge
OL,14,Feach night as well as the tunnel being
OL,15,Fclosed.
OL,17,FOn Wednesday and Thursday 10 and 11
OL,18,FJuly, the M4's eastbound carriageway
OL,19,Fwill be shut between between those
OL,20,Ftimes.
