OL,3,CTravellers to face disruption as
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel to shut
OL,6,FA GWR spokesperson announced: "Track
OL,7,Frenewal and essential drainage work
OL,8,Fwill affect all train services via the
OL,9,FSevern Tunnel with no direct trains
OL,10,Fbetween Bristol and South Wales.
OL,12,F"Trains between London and South Wales
OL,13,Fwill be diverted via Gloucester and as
OL,14,Fa result these services won't stop at
OL,15,FBristol Parkway. A limited number of
OL,16,Ftrains will be running between Bristol
OL,17,FParkway and London Paddington in the
OL,18,Fmorning and the evening only.
