OL,3,CTravellers to face disruption as
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel to shut
OL,6,F"Trains will run between Bristol
OL,7,FParkway and Portsmouth Harbour via
OL,8,FBristol Temple Meads, plus between
OL,9,FBristol Temple Meads and Taunton,
OL,10,FPlymouth or Penzance.
OL,12,F"Other train services will still be
OL,13,Frunning between Bristol Temple Meads
OL,14,For Bristol Parkway and Gloucester -
OL,15,Fchange at Gloucester for trains to
OL,16,FSouth Wales. Transport for Wales and
OL,17,FCrossCountry train services to/from
OL,18,FSouth Wales via Gloucester or
OL,19,FCheltenham Spa are unaffected by the
OL,20,FSevern Tunnel closure."
